info.description:
# readee

Library for export webpage to reader mode html.

## usage

```
import readee
beautiful_soup_html = readee.export(url = webpage_url)
```

optional args:
- content: raw webpage, will skip url fetching
- list_replace: will replace list, usually for telegraph export

## how to install

`pip3 install readee`
